## Summary
This documentation explains how to sync user data from Amplitude to third-party destinations using three methods: on-demand syncs (one-off), automated syncs (scheduled), and real-time syncs (minute-by-minute updates), with detailed instructions on creating syncs, viewing sync details, troubleshooting discrepancies, and understanding sync history reports.

